International King's Table Incsaid it named Everett F. Jefferson president and chiefoperating officer.    The company said Jefferson was previously president andchief operating officer of Marriott Corp's &lt;MHS> Straw HatPizza unit.    It said he assumes the positions from Roger W. Houmes, whowill continue as chairman and chief executive officer of thecompany, which operates a chain of 82 restaurants in the West. Reuter&#3;